OL,7,FA father whose family were forced to
OL,8,Fstay with relatives after being left
OL,9,Fwithout heating for five days says the
OL,10,Fwater company blamed for the disruption
OL,11,Fshould be "held to account".
OL,13,FJames Burdett lives in one of around
OL,14,F2,000 homes in the Sheffield suburb of
OL,15,FStannington which were left without
OL,16,Fcentral heating after a Yorkshire Water
OL,17,Fmain burst on Friday, sending hundreds
OL,18,Fof thousands of litres of water
OL,19,Fflooding into the gas network.
